#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 1.9 Pilindavacchattheragāthā → piḷindavacchattheragāthā (bj)
msgctxt "thag1.9:4.1"
msgid "1.9 Pilindavacchattheragāthā"
msgstr "1.9. Pilindavaccha"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="vns" id="vns9"></a><a class="vnp" id="vnp9"></a>
#. VAR: durāgataṃ → nāpagataṃ (s2, s3, pts1-2)
msgctxt "thag1.9:5.1"
msgid "“Svāgataṃ na durāgataṃ,"
msgstr "It was welcome, not unwelcome,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: Nayidaṃ → nedaṃ (pts2)
msgctxt "thag1.9:5.2"
msgid "Nayidaṃ dumantitaṃ mama;"
msgstr "the advice I got was good."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.9:5.3"
msgid "Saṃvibhattesu dhammesu,"
msgstr "Of things which are shared,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.9:5.4"
msgid "Yaṃ seṭṭhaṃ tadupāgamin”ti."
msgstr "I encountered the best."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
#. VAR: pilindavaccho → piḷindavaccho (bj)
msgctxt "thag1.9:6.1"
msgid "Itthaṃ sudaṃ āyasmā pilindavaccho thero gāthaṃ abhāsitthāti."
msgstr "It was thus that this verse was recited by the senior venerable Pilindavaccha."
